Cell["\<\
Integrate longer in time to observe saturation.
Only plot to an end time for which the integration worked (solutions may \
diverge to infinity).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8885043420944557`*^9, 3.888504354214511*^9}, {
  3.888504461570718*^9, 3.8885045133511066`*^9}, {3.982853592727899*^9, 
